skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: find it
des:
Ever spent days searching for your the ski goggles because you can't remember where you put them last time you went skiing? Well now you can ask Alexa! Simply tell alexa where you put the stuff you only need every so often so she can help you find it again!

Please note, there will be items that are not recognised by the skill please leave a review listing the items you would like adding and I will try to accommodate you.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
